{
  "stem": "16442.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 397.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were five people put in there, five of us in one row, in one [? pritch. ?] So actually, in each row, there were 15 people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to sleep one head, one foot, one head, one foot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And when we started asking questions, they said, don't ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You want to know where your parents are, where your relatives are?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see the flame?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you smell this smell?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's where they are burning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were shocked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were absolutely numb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We just had to lay in those beds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every morning, about 5 o'clock, we had to get up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And 6 o'clock, we had to stand in line outside, which was called 'saal appel.' That meant they had to count us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After they counted us, which was maybe for about an hour, we went back to our so-called-- the barrack.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they gave us for breakfast a so-called-- it was called coffee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was more like dirty dishwater.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to drink that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, every night, we we're getting a small piece of bread, which had to be divided into five.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] If you looked real good, you could look through the slices.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's how thin they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was our food for the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once a week, we used to get a very, very thin slice of wurst, which was like a salami, but very thin, or a very, very small piece of cheese.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But otherwise, during the whole week, we would get this piece of bread, which was sliced into five, and this so-called coffee.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
